{"tid":1646328,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"太妍、IU同時宣布回歸！　網驚「前面還有個音源女王Heize」橫掃年末音源榜","createTime":"2019-10-11T09:08:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T01:32:47.000Z","uid":34643,"like":17,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"262e5350e8fa8d3ebd9223e2934322158dc39c5a","tid":1646328,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:08:40.000Z","msg":"南韓歌手太妍和IU同天發佈全新專輯預告照，2人這次的風格都有超大突破引起熱烈討論，也讓人忍不住讚嘆音源的兩大女王竟然同時回歸，2019年底可以飽享耳福了。<br />\n<br />\n從2017年推出《Palette》時隔2年多的時間，IU於10日宣布將以第5張迷你專輯《Love poem》回歸，預告照中採夢幻柔光的濾鏡，搭配出道以來首次挑戰的藍色頭髮，在白藍玫瑰中綻放美貌。她曾在11周年見面會上說道，原本想做得和《CHAT-SHIRE》走獨特風格，但在10周年演唱會獲得了滿滿的力量，因此新專輯有了新的方向，這次的歌曲將比以往都還要溫暖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4432/4432039.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4432%2F4432039.jpg&h=88f4b5d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IU出道以來首次藍髮造型。（圖／翻攝自IU推特）<br />\n<br />\n不只如此，同天另一音源女王太妍也釋出了全新專輯《PURPOSE》的預告照，不如以往露臉拍攝，而是只露出下半臉和美肩，搭配橘紅色強烈光線有如油畫，另一張則是撩起頭髮露出刺在脖子背後的刺青，上面所刺的正是這次的專輯名稱《PURPOSE》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4432/4432041.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4432%2F4432041.jpg&h=3f70c3a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4432/4432040.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4432%2F4432040.jpg&h=f3dac337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲太妍《PURPOSE》預告照。（圖／翻攝自太妍IG）<br />\n<br />\n事實上，太妍脖子後方「Purpose」是2017年刺的刺青，曾在到國外展開街頭演唱的節目《beginagain3》談到其中意義：「不想人生活得沒有意義」。<br />\n<br />\n兩大女王的回歸掀起了一陣熱烈討論外，其實另一音源女王Heize將在10月13日以第五張迷你專輯《晚秋》回歸，加上將在10月22日回歸的太妍，11月回歸的IU，連續3大音源女王的回歸也被盛讚為「征服下半年音源排行榜的3大女子旋風」、「秋天女王們的回歸」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4432/4432042.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4432%2F4432042.jpg&h=b1ffc44a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Heize將以《晚秋》在13日回歸樂壇。（圖／翻攝自Heize臉書）<br />\n<br />\n▼Heize將以主打曲《掉落的落葉也&hellip;》在13日回歸樂壇。（影片／取自Heize official YouTube，如遭刪除請見諒）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GzQ1FebwQHI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGzQ1FebwQHI&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcqCfq%2BeyIt6E%2B7HnZU0UyvE%3D&h=856ef94b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GzQ1FebwQHI</a><blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"af927dd975be65fb60806f3961ed5daed7dec95b","tid":1646328,"uid":56701,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:爭咩吖...一齊合唱香港之歌吖....笨!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:爭咩吖....一齊合唱榮光歸香港吖...笨!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:爭咩吖...一齊合唱靈光雞香窩吖笨!"},{"pid":"fb95c3e9d579a5cdee776741e310edcfb84b39bd","tid":1646328,"uid":143093,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"af927dd975be65fb60806f3961ed5daed7dec95b","tid":1646328,"uid":56701,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:爭咩吖...一齊合唱香港之歌吖....笨!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:爭咩吖....一齊合唱榮光歸香港吖...笨!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:爭咩吖...一齊合唱靈光雞香窩吖笨!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:21:37.000Z","msg":"😅..."},{"pid":"05f5e1ecff1c476e3821e23a77a70ffd5e9e03ee","tid":1646328,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:21:47.000Z","msg":"我老婆越黎越靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361bc0d1e7c6371cc0c6985a70b80a53df1d6d07","tid":1646328,"uid":34643,"like":15,"dislike":20,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:26:02.000Z","msg":"btw, rip太妍, rip Heize"},{"pid":"1cb82d5665c3cf29e8f05c60ee81bb088eea798d","tid":1646328,"uid":18